{"tid":1677301,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[建議]米豬連三星制度","createTime":"2019-10-27T04:30:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-27T17:58:21.000Z","uid":320717,"like":10,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"0c6958b3b563df71f6bb7df9d1881ae60a974f2c","tid":1677301,"uid":320717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T04:30:35.000Z","msg":"米豬連一星: 在店面貼上小型文宣<br />\n米豬連二星: 在店面預留大量地方給文宣組(如明顯連儂檣, 大型抗爭藝術, 單據印上抗爭口號)<br />\n米豬連三星: 達到米豬連二星, 並每月向抗爭相關組織(如立場, 星火) 捐款 (以店員工數計算 * 300元計算)<br />\n<br />\n由每區文宣組執行, 每月檢查, 如有假冒即當藍店處理<br />\n各藍黃店apps 請加入己認證米豬連商店名單, 各位亦請盡量只到有米豬連認證的商店消費"},{"pid":"859ac5964b2da70058aff31c547b727a9686d1dc","tid":1677301,"uid":4574,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T04:31:50.000Z","msg":"三星:<br />\n龍門 唇茶"},{"pid":"358cbcb686d2d78debc018953a0ed739a8ac09eb","tid":1677301,"uid":222305,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T04:38:47.000Z","msg":"黃<br />\n深黃<br />\n金"},{"pid":"6d75264b6bb6100493fdac3c8077f11dc7ed823b","tid":1677301,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T04:41:46.000Z","msg":"米豬連三星將會有連登仔保護<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ca95221d1a4f47c29346ae7c7e3ff565f951945","tid":1677301,"uid":320717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6d75264b6bb6100493fdac3c8077f11dc7ed823b","tid":1677301,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T04:41:46.000Z","msg":"米豬連三星將會有連登仔保護<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T04:55:15.000Z","msg":"最好的保護方法係我地的銀包<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"064168399f56015f2211e3647312f33bb851d136","tid":1677301,"uid":254551,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T05:07:32.000Z","msg":"分級制會令黃店有比較，達唔到本身效果"},{"pid":"d8cf4dee47fd42425d1696f6606c923c206ad9de","tid":1677301,"uid":320717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"064168399f56015f2211e3647312f33bb851d136","tid":1677301,"uid":254551,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T05:07:32.000Z","msg":"分級制會令黃店有比較，達唔到本身效果"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T05:14:05.000Z","msg":"係鼓勵黃店更用力支持行動<br />\n現時的黃/藍制度有點唔公平, 好多時都係傳聞XXX 店幾個月前做過什麼好/壞事就算<br />\n我睇黃店揾黃店APPS, 去到一點黃店的氣氛都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果真係有心黃, 貼些少文宣有幾難?"},{"pid":"ff35098ce222df8de1b77ee07088dbc369ee8db3","tid":1677301,"uid":67505,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T05:17:49.000Z","msg":"龍門又係黃唇茶又係黃<br />\n一啲ig嘅黃店就咁寫住「喺黃店list」就算，冇文宣冇行為支持過又係黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60fa8559d83581274f9316c43ee6414cfe4b3c51","tid":1677301,"uid":320717,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ff35098ce222df8de1b77ee07088dbc369ee8db3","tid":1677301,"uid":67505,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T05:17:49.000Z","msg":"龍門又係黃唇茶又係黃<br />\n一啲ig嘅黃店就咁寫住「喺黃店list」就算，冇文宣冇行為支持過又係黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T05:23:00.000Z","msg":"exactly~~<br />\n所以要認證, 過去有幫手, 可以叫做黃, 但現在仍持續幫手的, 先可以有米豬連。 <br />\n比黃店一些incentive, 佢地先會更落力幫手。係又黃唔係又黃, 令人分唔到邊D 先係真正的深黃"},{"pid":"422dfc387a63353320c27b8ead776e4d0d3aeec8","tid":1677301,"uid":254551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T05:43:27.000Z","msg":"認證係一回事<br />\n分級係一回事<br />\n希望樓主諗清楚d關係先<br />\n或者可以考慮下參考現有制度<br />\n了解多d利害關係"},{"pid":"2bcff1e878cf4bffa0b501b315e61137b27c9cf3","tid":1677301,"uid":230043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T10:13:25.000Z","msg":"獵人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a21ecd3c665277597f17f8c45a257b41f0e346cb","tid":1677301,"uid":12946,"like":0,"dislike":